Detailed Description

cvmx_stx::_dip_cnt

Notes: * DIPMAX This counts the number of consecutive DIP2 states in which the the received DIP2 is bad. The expected range is 1-15 cycles with the value of 0 meaning disabled.

* FRMMAX This counts the number of consecutive unexpected framing patterns (11) states. The expected range is 1-15 cycles with the value of 0 meaning disabled.
